{
  "name": "Trendlines",
  "summary": "<p>每一个 <strong>Trendline</strong> 对象都代表图表中的趋势线。趋势线显示系列中数据的趋势或方向。</p>\n<p><b class=\"mainheaders\">示例</b></p><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*以下示例显示 Chart1 上第一系列的趋势线数。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例给 Sheet1 中嵌入式图表一中的第一个系列添加线性趋势线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Sheet1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>().<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlLinear, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">null</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Linear Trend&quot;</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*下例更改工作表一上嵌入式图表一中第一个系列的趋势线类型。如果该系列没有趋势线，本示例将失败。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Worksheets</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Type</span> = xlMovingAvg\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
  "description": "<p>指定的数据系列中所有 <strong>Trendline</strong> 对象的集合。</p>\n",
  "category": "et",
  "properties": [
    {
      "name": "Application",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>如果不使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个 <strong>Application</strong>对象，该对象表示 ET 应用程序。如果使用对象识别符，则该属性返回一个表示指定对象（可对一个 OLE 自动操作对象使用本属性来返回该对象的应用程序）创建者的 <strong>Application</strong> 对象。只读。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<p>本示例显示一条有关创建 <code>myObject</code> 的应用程序的消息。</p>\n<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">TEST</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>)\n{\n   <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> myObject = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ActiveWorkbook</span>\n   <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">if</span>(myObject.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Value</span> == <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;ET&quot;</span>){\n       <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n   }\n   <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">else</span>{\n       <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">MsgBox</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;This is not an ET Application object.&quot;</span>)\n   }\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "Application",
      "readonly": true
    },
    {
      "name": "Count",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>返回一个 <strong>Long</strong> 值，它代表集合中对象的数量。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示第一张工作表上第一个图表的第二个数据系列趋势线的个数。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> series = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(series.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>().<span class=\"hljs-property\">Count</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "type": "number（int4 精度）",
      "readonly": true
    }
  ],
  "functions": [
    {
      "name": "Add",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>创建新的趋势线。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例在 Chart1 上创建新的线性趋势线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">ActiveWorkbook</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>().<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>()\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例在第一张工作表上的第一个图表的第二个数据系列创建新的趋势线。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> series = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    series.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>().<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Add</span>(xlMovingAvg, <span class=\"hljs-number\">3</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">4</span>, <span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>, <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Type",
          "type": "XlTrendlineType",
          "description": "<p>趋势线类型。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Order",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>如果 Type 为 xlPolynomial。趋势线顺序号。必须为 2 到 6 之间的整数（包括 2 和 6）。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Period",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>如果 Type 为 xlMovingAvg。趋势线周期。必须为大于 1，而小于正添加趋势线的数据系列中数据点个数的整数。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Forward",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>趋势线向前延伸的周期数目（或散点图中的单位个数）。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Backward",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>趋势线向后延伸的周期数目（或散点图中的单位个数）。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Intercept",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>趋势线的截距。如果省略此参数，则由回归分析自动设置截距。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "DisplayEquation",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>如果为 True，则在图表中显示趋势线的公式（与 R 平方值显示在同一数据标签中）。默认值为 False。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "DisplayRSquared",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>如果为 True，则在图表中显示趋势线的 R 平方值（与公式显示��同一数据标签中）。默认值为 False。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        },
        {
          "name": "Name",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>作为文本的趋势线名称。如果省略此参数，则由 ET 生成名称。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        }
      ],
      "returns": "<p>一个代表新趋势线的 Trendline 对象。</p>\n"
    },
    {
      "name": "Item",
      "summary": "",
      "description": "<p>从集合中返回一个对象。</p>\n",
      "examples": "<div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*本示例对 Chart1 中的趋势线向前和向后延伸的单位数进行设置。本示例应在包含具有趋势线的单个序列的 2D 柱形图上运行。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> trendline = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Charts</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;Chart1&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>().<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>)\n    trendline.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Forward</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">5</span>\n    trendline.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Backward</span> = <span class=\"hljs-number\">0.5</span>\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div id=\"vstable\"><table width=\"100%\"><tbody><tr><th>示例代码<span class=\"copy\" onclick=\"copyCode(this)\">复制</span></th></tr><tr><td><pre><code><span class=\"hljs-comment\">/*此示例显示第一张工作表上的第一个图表的第二个数据系列索引为2的趋势线名称。*/</span>\n<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">test</span>(<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) {\n    <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">let</span> series = <span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Application</span>.<span class=\"hljs-property\">Worksheets</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">ChartObjects</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">1</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Chart</span>.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">SeriesCollection</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>)\n    <span class=\"hljs-title function_\">alert</span>(series.<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Trendlines</span>().<span class=\"hljs-title class_\">Item</span>(<span class=\"hljs-number\">2</span>).<span class=\"hljs-property\">Name</span>)\n}</code></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></div>",
      "parameters": [
        {
          "name": "Index",
          "type": "any",
          "description": "<p>对象的索引号。</p>\n",
          "optional": true
        }
      ],
      "returns": "<p>包含在集合中的一个 Trendline 对象。</p>\n"
    }
  ]
}